{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the girls say, she can play it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, you can play?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, what can you play?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, 'La Danza'.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she says, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she played, and she was so happy, the teacher, that I learned, that already we will be start playing with the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was so excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said to her, when I-- when we-- we played-- and then she said to the-- the teacher said, you know, her mother wanted her to play the double bass when she was in Greece.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she didn't have the chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See now they are human.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They suddenly get human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They say, where's your mother now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He asked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The teacher says, she went through the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, [GERMAN]-- in German, means shame.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, now he's sorry, because he sees we are human, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I say, I'm 14.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, one day-- he says, when you get out of here, you may earn your living with that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we all look at each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Are we ever going to get out of here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, and that, which is the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got the job-- this is how-- what I got out of here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I use this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the thing is, how they become so human all of a sudden when they see you are a person, that you can talk, and you can-- you are normal.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That-- well, anyway, we-- so I became-- now nobody-- I couldn't lose the job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because nobody played the double bass-- just me-- the accordion into the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I still played marches alternating with the other one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One day I'll play, one day she would play, because it was very cold outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
